defaultWhat are the corporate governance concerns raised by the number of extractive industries companies listed in the UK? Are there reputational risks for the UK and UK financial institutions in being a centre for such businesses?defaultC
defaultompanies come to the LSE to benefit from the UK’s respected corporate governance regime. 
